# Quality checks after code changes

After making any code change in this project, always run these commands before finishing:

1. `npm run lint:fix` — auto-fix Biome issues (formatting, import order, safe fixes)
2. `npm run lint` — verify no remaining Biome errors
3. `npm run type-check` — verify TypeScript types

If `lint` or `type-check` fails, fix the reported issues and re-run until both pass.

Do not skip these checks, even for small edits.
